OL,3,CPaedophile who fled to 'paradise' for
OL,4,C27 years finally stands trial
OL,6,FA former Scout leader who went on the
OL,7,Frun after being accused of child sex
OL,8,Foffences told police he had been
OL,9,Fliving in "paradise" after returning
OL,10,Ffrom Thailand after 27 years.
OL,12,FRichard Burrows, 80, fled the UK after
OL,13,Fbeing due in court in December 1997, a
OL,14,Fjury at Chester Crown Court was told.
OL,16,FHe told his brother "not all
OL,17,Fpaedophiles are the same", as he
OL,18,Fplanned his return to the UK in March
OL,19,F2024.
