OL,3,CPaedophile who fled to 'paradise' for
OL,4,C27 years finally stands trial
OL,6,FMr Connor said Burrows was first
OL,7,Farrested in April 1997 and his house
OL,8,Fin Birmingham was searched.
OL,10,FA number of magazines showing
OL,11,Fadolescent and pre-pubescent boys
OL,12,Fengaged in sex were found stitched
OL,13,Finside one of his jackets.
OL,15,FHe was charged with child sexual
OL,16,Foffences and was due to appear at
OL,17,FChester Crown Court on December 8 1997.
OL,19,FWhen he failed to attend, a warrant
OL,20,Fwas issued for his arrest.
