OL,3,CPaedophile who fled to 'paradise' for
OL,4,C27 years finally stands trial
OL,6,FBurrows had fled to Thailand using the
OL,7,Fname Peter Leslie Smith, having cloned
OL,8,Fan acquaintance's identity and
OL,9,Fobtained a passport in that name.
OL,11,FHe was arrested at Heathrow Airport
OL,12,Fwhen he returned to the UK on the eve
OL,13,Fof his 80th birthday last March.
OL,15,F"Having enjoyed 27 years in paradise,
OL,16,Fto quote his description of where he
OL,17,Fhad spent his time on the run," Mr
OL,18,FConnor said.
OL,20,FThe trial is expected to last up to
OL,21,Ffive weeks.
